      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IVORY HAMADA (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Goblin (22.32) in a Grade 4/5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Top prospect. BAILIESTON (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (30.93) last time in a Grade 5 at The Meadows. Form here sound including three wins. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. FLUENT ACTION (6) was out of placings last time (24.31) at Bendigo in a Grade 4, finishing fourth and beaten 7 lengths. Has three wins already from this draw. Looks one of the chances. GRAND PERFECTION (4) is another with top-three prospects.",
